==English==
===Verb===
'''to explain''' ([[explains]], [[explained]], [[explaining]])

# To give a sufficiently detailed report about the reason for something, about why something happened, about a causal chain of events.
# To give a sufficiently detailed report about how something works, about how elements in a system interact.
# To give a sufficiently detailed report about how to do something, about the steps which need to be accomplished in order to accomplish a certain goal.
# To give a valid excuse for some past behavior.

